Google is launching a First Amendment challenge to the U.S. government's gag order on information its forced to give .
of course this will be the only way this gets even remotely resolved . by having our corporate overlords challenge our government overlords .
How do we protect ourselves, or more likely our children, from the next generation who runs google or other information gathering mega companies?
